Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: Quote from: Utrojestan on October 15, 2018, 12:40:25 PM Hello, can elama compete with other AI? I would like something new and impressive!  It is a clear fact you stated that AI market is now in great competition. IT giants all over the world from Google to Alibaba are heavily investing in AI with phenomenal expansion of AI market. The point of interest to make on current status is that it is still a newer market with huge potential to grow. Market-base of AI market is still expanding and growing every year, which means it is not a zero-sum market with plenty of fresh opportunities for new AI project to take initiatives.  Competitiveness of AI ELA compared to other blockchain-based AI or even other conventional centralized AI services is well addressed in our whitepaper so I wouldn't go too deep with that subject. ELAMACHAIN Platform's comprehensive eco-system which can fully integrate AI-use and users' daily life will bring possibly first functional Hyperledger-based AI to the world with incomparable benefit.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: ELA Coin(ELAC) is rewarded to AI ELA service users as compensation to the contribution to AI system. Raising affinity level with AI(which would be numerically shown in AI app display) through communicating with AI ELA would be one of the ways to get ELAC from the platform. Also, there would be ELA missions handed out to each users, which would be personally customized to bring best benefit both to users and AI data collection, and additional ELAC will be rewarded in that way as well.  Policy on number amount of ELAC for rewards system is currently under discussion. We acknowledge the delicate nature of rewards system, so we are working hard to set up the right number.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: With no presentation of any sources backing your claim, I have to humbly respond to your comment with this: You don't know what you are talking about.  With strong growth in AI market worldwide, need for good targeted AI is more than ever before. Integration of AI technology with other industries would only deepen as time passes by,  just like blockchain technology has done so past few years.  Functioning blockchain-based AI in that sense would hardly "lose relevance" in at least foreseeable future. Plus, if you truly tried to share our vision of the project and understand the magnitude of its reach,  you would know how unrealistic you were when you mentioned "any plans for new developments."

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: AI ELA would be available to anyone. For limits, we may have to say it is upto you how you form relationship with AI ELA. More you allow AI ELA to learn about you, less barriers and limitations it would have.  That being said, AI ELA service would not offer exclusive privileges to investors. First, it is better for AI to grow in general. Second, since the AI ELA would be essentially open-source AI project, allowing privileged conditions  for AI services to certain groups would be self-contradictory.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: Quote from: Nasivini67 on October 13, 2018, 01:48:04 PM Will your service be in Chinese and English? Do you plan to introduce other languages for the convenience of all users?  Language support is one of the major points Elamachain takes seriously. The service is most likely to be available on following 3 languages: English, Chinese, Korean. However, we do understand that spread of use can only come with variety of language support for global users. What we need to consider, though, is that NLP(Natural Language Process) which AI ELA would make use of is highly sensitive to each different languages and adding new language is no small project. Please be noted that the team is aware of the issue and aims to solve.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: First thing first : Name of AI form Elamachain platform is ELA, not elama.   What we seek to achieve from AI ELA is to develop emotionally responsive dialogue system which can positively interact with users in deeper level. User-AI bond is key to success of AI not just for user satisfaction but also collecting credible data for AI growth. In that sense, main function of AI ELA would be responsive dialogue-based relationship with users.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: Again, Elamachain team is consisted of multi-national background members including American, Korea, Chinese. Core members are indeed primarily Korean. I have no idea where you got the information - or impression - that Elamachain project is from "Chinese team," so I suggest you do your research better.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: The name of AI is ELA, not elama.   There is no pre-configured gender for AI ELA. (No need to do so, by the way)  But you could choose your own setting of your AI to cope with your preference, so in a sense, yes, it can be a girl for you maybe.  The primary source of collecting user preference is dialogue between users and ELA. ELA would adopt Natural Language Process so that it can understand and keep the communication with users in relevance. More you talk and interact with ELA, better it can accurately "guess" your preferences, of course.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform

Fundamental difference would be Hyperledger-based architecture which grants high-speed transactions and data transfer thanks to its private-blockchain-like property. Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: Please kindly refer to our previous answer.  Quote from: elamachain on September 21, 2018, 01:11:11 AM Quote from: RodGerols on September 20, 2018, 05:53:05 PM It was very interesting to read Whitepapper, but not fully understand the project. Will your service be free or will you have to pay?  Elamachain platform is planned to be released in form of web and mobile application, and no fee would be charged for installing and/or using services from our platform, at least in principle in our policy. However, there can be services exclusively available to ELA Coin holders or services that can only be paid in ELA Coin. Plus, needless to say, the policy is subject to change for circumstances.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: Elamachain aims to develop comprehensive AI that can meet every possible needs, but the priority would lie on being personal assistant. So yes, suggesting ways to lose weight or guiding users to help with payment is very likely to be part of our AI features, at least in the long run.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: We've designed a sequence of user entry to AI service, collecting basic information from, say, questionnaires, in it's initial stage. From that on, two major things needed for AI to tell one's emotion would come from constant interaction between AI and users and analysis on data from such activities. So no, you will not need to fill out questionnaires or be forced to answer rather pointless questions. AI ELA would adopt to deeper level of user preferences mostly through natural language conversation and specifically formated ELA missions. Ultimately it will grow to be capable of identifying key parameters of user behavior, notably key words used in conversation with ELA.

Author: elamachain
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ELAMACHAIN : Emotional AI Platform
Body: We do not underestimate the magnitude of our project and acknowledge this project is something to be carried out in long run. What we vision ourselves with ELAMACHAIN platform is comprehensive ecosystem centered with AI, and path to achieve such goal has to overcome many obstacles. That is why we have prepared what can be done first, payment infrastructure, which not only fuctions as a vital part of ecosystem but also supports the sustainability of the project. Building a Good AI as you said is not an easy task and has to be done step-by-step. The launch of AI-based Elamachain platform is the beginning of reaching the goal, not the finish line.
